{"tid":1083811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"幾多個翻撻左又真係可以走到結婚再生仔","createTime":"2019-03-30T02:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T07:46:16.000Z","uid":245582,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"31e7fae7f26c30037005ca08c10adb8dd6585fbb","tid":1083811,"uid":245582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:15:44.000Z","msg":"分得手就代表其中一個已經唔愛，真係有幾多個係幾年後發現真係好愛對方，想翻撻<br />\n<br />\n講分手嘅想翻撻，最後可能因為類似嘅原因再分開，又或者因為要用更多時間去令對方重新好似以前咁無芥蒂，覺得攰喇，最後頂唔順一味得自己付出。又可能發現對方已經無以前咁愛你，對你咁好，覺得對方變左，最後又搞到分手<br />\n<br />\n被分手嘅，如果仲愛，當初一定會有做過好多挽回嘅野，會唔會覺得自己係對方甚至對方屋企人面前好尷尬。又或者，係咪真係可以忘記對方係講分手嘅時候所有令你傷心嘅野。   係咪始終都會有條刺係到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>真心想聽大家復合嘅分享<br />\n又當係比個提醒啲諗住復回嘅人</strong>"},{"pid":"94bd40f52916dbd9cf7e8ae57f5408fcac581696","tid":1083811,"uid":35815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:20:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1589eaa1f49b75b372fa56e0e99fdbd7e2369096","tid":1083811,"uid":245582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94bd40f52916dbd9cf7e8ae57f5408fcac581696","tid":1083811,"uid":35815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:20:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"施主 此話何解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fedf40ed0262dbf4460d3e10142759ba33093b9","tid":1083811,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d2a0fb197fb375eead75316f67bbbc63b10ec5d","tid":1083811,"uid":207702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"我都想翻撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bf2a83c4bcb219346c97577ca78a308fb24fbc","tid":1083811,"uid":179548,"li